    "shortDescription": "<p>You make the target an asymptomatic carrier for a host of virulent diseases. Creatures that end their turn adjacent to the target must succeed at a Fortitude save or be affected as if by the spell <i>contagion</i>. The target itself does not become diseased, and suffers no ill effects from this spell. Once <i>plague bearer</i> ends, the target is no longer contagious, though any creature it infected remains diseased.</p>"
